===============================
Kingbird Dashboard
===============================

User Interface for Kingbird

* Free software: Apache license
* Source: http://git.openstack.org/cgit/openstack/kingbird-dashboard
* Bugs: http://bugs.launchpad.net/kingbird-dashboard

